# Breaking Changes

- Removed the experimental language interop from `v5.6.0`. All `include/glaze/interop/*` headers, the `src/interop` target, and associated tests have been deleted, and the `glaze_BUILD_INTEROP` CMake option no longer exists. https://github.com/stephenberry/glaze/pull/1976
- Renamed the dynamically typed `glz::json_t` to `glz::generic` (`include/glaze/json/generic.hpp`). https://github.com/stephenberry/glaze/pull/1984
- Streaming HTTP clients now surface server-side failures as category-aware `std::error_code` instances via `glz::http_status_category()`. Handlers that assumed generic networking errors should read the status code with `glz::http_status_from`.

